data.description: Beautiful home on a large lot, well maintained in the perfect location. Living room in the front of the home and Kitchen window out the back so you can watch the kids or pup play.  A stones through away from Hayes park, Sunnyslope Dog Park just a walk down the street and just a bikes ride away from Glendale Community College. Less then 6 miles away from the beautiful Westgate Shopping Area and State Farm Stadium. Talk about location, location, location, it couldn't get any better than this!
